---
title: HelloHero: Italian Beef & Pork Fusilli with Baby Leaves & Cheddar Cheese
description: Pasta with a cheesy tomato sauce, veggies and the combo of beef and pork, all packed into one amazing piled-high pasta. If that’s what you were hoping for then this dish won’t disappoint you!

*We’ve replaced the orecchiette in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6708528f10eac7b3edfeddd1-7831d96e.jpeg
